The Role of Reaffirmation and Direct Matching in Metaphor
　The Role of Reaffirmation and Direct Matching in Metaphor
　　Where "felt meaning" is invoked from a symbol, it is reaffirmed.
　　Direct Match "Is Time Money?" No!
　　　Metaphor: "Time is gold" "(direct collation) Eh, time is not gold. What is this person trying to say... well, that time is as precious as gold!"
